INforAMA,is,the,Information,Engine,for,Advanced,Mobility,Applications,It,can,be,integrated,with,an,in,car,device,to,keep,track,of,the,car,s,position,speed,route,and,other,information,INforAMA,is,provided,by,the,HiGrids,Foundation,which,is,in,the,business,of,developing,and,implementing,projects,in,the,field,of,intelligent,transport,systems